# Attack 05 – Scheduled Task Persistence

## Objective

Simulate persistence using Windows Scheduled Tasks.

## Attack

Created and executed a scheduled task using schtasks.exe.

## Detection

PowerShell and Windows process creation logs recorded scheduled task activity.

## MITRE ATT&CK

- T1053.005 – Scheduled Task

## Investigation

Reviewed process creation events and confirmed scheduled task execution.

## Outcome

Scheduled task activity was successfully monitored.
